snippet.title: Magenta Horizon Act 1 Announcement Trailer (Re-uploaded)
snippet.description:
Magenta Horizon is a 2D action game Heavily inspired by Devil May Cry, Hollow Knight, several arcade games, and Tim Burton movies.
The game is solely created by myself, and Act 1 will be available soon in Itch.io for free.

#sidescroller #indiegames #characteractiongames

[Edit on 2021-10-17]
From now on, Magenta Horizon is available at itch.io: https://maddison-baek.itch.io/magenta-horizon
